13. Scoring Additions

Add three new scores beyond survivability:

def metabolism_scores(pattern):
    return {
        "salvage_value": estimate_salvage_value(pattern),
        "hazard_level": estimate_hazard_level(pattern),
        "antidote_potential": estimate_antidote_potential(pattern),
        "meta_pattern_density": estimate_meta_pattern_density(pattern),
    }

Definitions
	•	salvage_value: how much useful structure remains
	•	hazard_level: how risky the pattern is if reused raw
	•	antidote_potential: how well it can generate a defense or replacement
	•	meta_pattern_density: how much this example teaches about a larger class

